## PLACEHOLDER REFERENCE

| Placeholder | Source | Example |
|---|---|---|
| `{{BRAND_NAME}}` | Official brand name, exact casing | `12eat唐人街外卖` |
| `{{BRAND_SLUG}}` | Lowercase alphanumeric, no spaces | `12eat` |
| `{{BRAND_NICHE}}` | One-sentence positioning | `Authentic Chinese food delivery` |
| `{{BRAND_MISSION}}` | Agent's core mission | `Generate posts that drive orders` |
| `{{MARKETS}}` | Target markets + languages | `North America (en) + 海外华人社区 (zh)` |
| ~~OWNER_LARK_ID~~ | Removed — all Lark users are team | — |
| `{{TRENDING_RADAR_URL}}` | Shared Lark Doc (default pre-filled) | `https://12eat-ai.sg.larksuite.com/docx/...` |
| `{{LARK_WORKSPACES_URL}}` | Vault parent folder (default pre-filled) | `https://12eat-ai.sg.larksuite.com/drive/...` |
| `{{VAULT_LARK_URL}}` | Created by Bootstrap via mcp.lark.drive | `https://12eat-ai.sg.larksuite.com/drive/folder/...` |
| `{{AMC_KANBAN_API_KEY}}` | AMC Kanban Agent API Key（Bearer Token）| `eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1...` |

> **社交媒体发布** 全部通过 AMC Kanban 完成，无需在本地配置任何第三方平台 API Key。
> 仅当 AMC Kanban 确实无法实现时，Agent 才自主寻找替代路径，并将原因和结果记录到 Kanban 任务。
> API 调用失败时必须执行 `fallback-execution` skill，通过其他 skill 和浏览器/RPA 路径完成工作。

